What are Variables?
    Variables are containers or boxes in the memory that can hold the data for us.
Why do wwe need Variables?
    Before we can ask the computer to do something for us, we need to store the information and instructions on a file then we feed those to the computer does that thing for us.
How to creaate the Variables (SyntaX)
     1) we need to tell the computer what type of box/container/variables we need
     2) we need to give a name to box.
